    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Formats of paintings, prints, photographs, sculptures, or other works or other things that fall within a small range of size for the norm. For example, the term is used to describe photographic film formats 35mm and smaller.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
